comment: Harris (ORL) puts his hand on the ball as Pachulia (MIL) jumps, causing Pachulia to return to the floor while both still in contact with the ball. Jump ball is assessed.
LHH shows Payton (ORL) cleanly strips Carter-Williams (MIL).

After communicating with the Replay Center, the contact by Payton (MIL) was ruled a common foul by the officials on the floor. Referees may review any foul called to determine if it meets the criteria for a Flagrant 1 or 2, common or technical foul.
Payton (ORL) makes contact with Carter-Williams (MIL) as he attempts his shot.
R-Slash shows slight contact by Dudley (MIL) to Harris (ORL) during his shot attempt that is incidental to his attempt to play him and does not affect his ability to take the shot.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Antetokounmpo (MIL) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Frye (ORL) commits a take foul on Middleton (MIL).
